---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About Us | SBHS Robotics 750">
    <div class="container">
        <header class="page-header">
            <h1 class="text-glow-gold">About South Brunswick Robotics</h1>
        </header>
        <div class="about-grid">
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-gradient-gold">Our Mission</h2>
                <p>Our mission is to foster a passion for science, technology, engineering, and mathematics (STEM) through competitive robotics. We provide a hands-on, student-led environment where members learn valuable technical and collaborative skills that prepare them for future careers.</p>

                <h2 class="text-gradient-gold" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Our History</h2>
                <p>Founded in 2012, South Brunswick Robotics has grown from a small club into a competitive robotics organization within New Jersey. We participate in the VEX Robotics Competition, reaching state and world championship levels through dedication and innovative design.</p>
            </div>
            <img src="/images/team-photo.jpg" alt="South Brunswick Robotics Team" style="border-radius: 0.5rem;"/>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>